'''Ahilyum''' (s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tnglizt]] : -{Helium}-) iga t [[Afrḍis akimyan|ufrḍis akimi]] lli mu gan tasdugmt n '''He''' d  uṭṭun afrḍas 2. Ur dar-s [[Aklu|akʷlu]], aḍu d tamimt, ur igi toxic, iga ulmig ''(-{inert}-)'', ar ittga agaz n yan ufrḍis ''(-{monoatomic gaz}-)'', d iga amzwaru ɣ trabut n igazn usmidn ''(the noble gas)'' ɣ [[taflwit tazdawant n ifrḍisn]].

'''Ahilyum''' iga wissin ifrḍisn ɣ tfssi d tugt ɣ umaḍal ([[Ahidrujin]] ad igan amzwaru ɣ tfssi d tugt), iga 24% n [[Tamtta|tmtta]], d unck mqqurn gis ittuskar s ''-{nuclear fusion}-'' n [[Ahidrujin|uhidrujin]] ɣ [[Itri|itran]].<ref>[[:en:Helium|Asuɣl zɣ Wikipidya tanglizt: Helium]]</ref>

